{
  "stem": "13141.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our work, as I mentioned before, we were the intermediary between the German authorities and the potential immigrants.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, if I say potential immigrants, many of those potential immigrants, they never made it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never made it not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on account of a lack of trying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried very, very hard, all of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But unfortunately at the time, there were very, very few countries, in fact, I must say there was none, maybe the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had that immigration quota, which was very limited.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And most people just couldn't make it, unless you had financial means, money outside of Germany, which, at that time, was prohibited to have outside of Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were supposed to bring everything you had outside of Germany, bring it back, which made it more difficult, too, I mean, to-- for transactions if you wanted to, to leave.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But unless you had money outside of Germany or you had very good contacts in the foreign countries, it was very difficult to, to get out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Nowadays, they're all big heroes, even including the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Pardon me for saying so, because I'm a US citizen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at the time, it was just banging your head against the wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were very few possibilities to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was too late too, already, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in 1939, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became more difficult as time went by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It became more and-- difficult and more difficult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I myself, I didn't have any contacts whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother had a, a cousin once-removed in the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But a letter took-- a letter at the time took about six weeks, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
